        <updateDate>2021-08-25T22:01:42Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This resolution encourages the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) to update certain guidance to clarify that individuals who are fully vaccinated against COVID-19 need not wear masks on public transportation networks. The resolution also recommends that the Transportation Security Administration align its mask requirements with such CDC guidance.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
